 generating a greater return to pay
its investors or attract new capital. This sort of prediction either demons=
trates the <em>schadenfreude </em>within the market, or the lack of broader=
 financial acuity=E2=80=94perhaps both.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bott=
om:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">It=E2=80=99s en=
