6d845733963c59ec8ff189337da85517c0c1da5a78" style=3D"text-decoration:underl=
ine;color:#d40000;">list</a> for 2025. Cats and cat memes are out, artist <=
strong>Nicole Eisenman</strong> told <em>Cultured</em> magazine. What=E2=80=
